{"tid":849774,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭欣宜支持性小眾 唔排除同女仔發展","createTime":"2018-10-06T03:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T02:13:48.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9d734b002f79e65addb998987ad37921b2ca8f8c","tid":849774,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gyXRCZh8zZGlaYjfPtQruA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20181003f162432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FgyXRCZh8zZGlaYjfPtQruA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20181003f162432.jpg&h=bf95eea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】鄭欣宜出席《一點粉紅》新聞發佈會，她表示一直支持該會的活動，很開心今年成為粉紅大使，希望可以令更多人理解和接受性小眾，同時教育下一代，讓他們知道不一樣並不可怕，每個人都有權利愛人。<br />\n<br />\n欣宜直認身邊有不少同性戀朋友，認為是平常事，不過沒有同性朋友追過她。她說：「大家都知我是直，我暫時都是喜歡男仔，但不排除將來會遇到好夾的女仔。」她又稱期待拍攝新歌《黑彩虹》的MV，因為歌曲不只關於愛情，又透露今次的MV在藝術方面有很大突破。"},{"pid":"b55b3990c361a14415cd8e433ee30aee2e0ad44f","tid":849774,"uid":38041,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:14:08.000Z","msg":"肥婆多是麻撚煩"},{"pid":"3cdc712180e05e26459a8c57bfb01997b6d963c6","tid":849774,"uid":161190,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:17:39.000Z","msg":"肥到條褲爆曬出嚟"},{"pid":"fa011b042b005e19d5c240e3caab51f62f7b29dc","tid":849774,"uid":87506,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:19:03.000Z","msg":"邊有男人要你阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e60da02bc38509effc77ab9ebd52766fb9a431c","tid":849774,"uid":213762,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T03:26:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a417c8873b1d4796a6e6881ee49c08314576e46","tid":849774,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06